snippet.title: Sherwood Extreme - Official Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Play FREE and Join a Faction: https://discord.com/invite/aeF2jEn
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1340180

Save Sherwood as Robin Hood: master of parkour and archery! Zipping, swinging, slow-mo sniping slaughter. Explore the kingdom solo or with friends in Co-Op for speed running and ridiculous action!

@cagestudios on all social media!
